### Test actualizar avistamiento con nueva imagen
PUT http://localhost:5167/api/sightings/{{sightingId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="cameraId"

{{cameraId}}
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="sightingTimeUtc"

2024-07-16T10:30:00Z
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="notes"

Avistamiento actualizado con nueva imagen - Prueba
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="newImageFile"; filename="test-image.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test-image.jpg
--boundary--

